videos.description: Trent Waters shows off the handles on his way into the teeth of FSU's defense.
videos.headline: Waters weaves way to bucket

videos.description: Anthony Polite spots up for a corner 3-ball to extend LSU's lead.
videos.headline: Polite nails transition 3-pointer

videos.description: Florida State's Trent Forrest drives baseline and is blocked by Emmit Williams.
videos.headline: Williams rejects Forrest's dunk attempt

videos.description: Trent Forrest goes coast-to-coast to send Florida State to overtime with LSU.
videos.headline: Forrest's layup sends it to OT

videos.description: Tremont Waters breaks down a defender and finishes with a smooth reverse layup.
videos.headline: Waters floats across the lane for reverse lay-in

videos.description: Mfiondu Kabengele launches a 3-pointer from the corner to win it for Florida State.
videos.headline: Kabengele's last-second 3 wins it for Seminoles
